snippet.textDisplay: This is so divine. I listened to the entire song with my eyes closed and swaying with the beats. The person on Tabla, hats off to him for maintaining the rhythm thru out the song. I play Tabla myself, I know, how difficult it is to play at that pace for 12 mins. No matter what I say in praise of Rahet Fateh Ali and Amjad Sabri, it will never be enough. Boon to music, Boon to humanity. God bless to the entire team of Coke Studio Pakistan, for coming up masterpieces like these.
